<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-5985] Paxos replay of in progress update is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5985</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we replay &lt;tt&gt;inProgress&lt;/tt&gt;, we need to refresh it with the newly prepared ballot, or it will be (correctly) rejected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
